# Include Version File

When making or committing code changes in this repository, always include `src/family_tasks_bot/version.py` in the change set.

- Before committing, check `src/family_tasks_bot/version.py` explicitly.
- If `src/family_tasks_bot/version.py` has local changes, stage and commit it together with the related code changes.
- Do not leave `src/family_tasks_bot/version.py` modified but uncommitted after a code-change commit.
